00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:28.800
Good.

00:07:31.959 --> 00:07:32.759
What are you doing?

00:07:32.759 --> 00:07:33.720
Let go of me!

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:38.040
Dare to kill someone on my territory?

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:59.120
I don't know anything.

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:00.720
Doesn't matter.

00:08:01.800 --> 00:08:03.120
Anyway, it's already recorded.

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:12.600
Gu Chenyu,

00:08:12.600 --> 00:08:13.959
we've taken care of it here.

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:16.120
Don't you have anything to say?

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:17.360
I didn't release the PR draft.

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:22.279
Let's go.

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:29.360
Yunyun.

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:30.800
There must be a misunderstanding here.

00:08:33.799 --> 00:08:34.799
Let's talk privately.

00:08:34.799 --> 00:08:35.960
What else is there to talk about?

00:08:36.600 --> 00:08:37.159
Yunyun.

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:37.679
Let's go.

00:08:37.679 --> 00:08:39.279
Give me a chance to explain.

00:08:45.960 --> 00:08:46.919
I swear,

00:08:46.919 --> 00:08:48.919
the PR department's orders weren't mine.

00:08:49.559 --> 00:08:50.399
I absolutely would never

00:08:50.399 --> 00:08:52.360
let anyone from Jiangxing Hotel
take the blame.

00:08:52.879 --> 00:08:54.600
I can't trust
what you're saying right now.

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:56.240
Fine.

00:08:56.879 --> 00:08:58.960
I will find out the truth
within two days.

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:04.879
Have you contacted that doctor already?

00:09:05.879 --> 00:09:06.960
Why are you asking?

00:09:08.799 --> 00:09:09.919
I've checked.

00:09:09.919 --> 00:09:11.200
He has a child

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.919
with severe congenital heart disease.

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:16.200
This year is the last chance
for surgery.

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:18.279
Originally, the child
was in the countryside,

00:09:18.279 --> 00:09:19.360
without money for surgery.

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:21.360
But recently,

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:23.600
