00:09:29.159 --> 00:09:29.799
Think about it.

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:31.759
If his daughter is in my hands,

00:09:31.759 --> 00:09:33.960
would he dare admit to you
that I ordered him to do it?

00:09:39.320 --> 00:09:40.039
Oh no.

00:09:40.039 --> 00:09:41.600
I locked him in Jiangxing Hotel.

00:09:41.919 --> 00:09:43.799
If someone wants him to die
in the hotel,

00:09:43.799 --> 00:09:45.490
Jiangxing Hotel will never
be able to clear its name.

00:09:45.559 --> 00:09:46.159
Don't panic.

00:09:49.960 --> 00:09:51.679
Since they planned this long ago,

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:53.720
then we will

00:09:55.039 --> 00:09:56.480
meet each move with a counter.

